1. Start DDEV.
2. Switch in git to the dev branch.
3. Create a new branch based on the dev branch with the prefix and name.
4. Begin with the implementation.
5. Check for linting errors for PHP, CSS and JavaScript.
6. Create unit/function tests for PHP and JavaScript.
7. Run the tests and adjust them if they fail. Repeat this until all tests are passed.
8. Create a changelog to record the implementation. Use always the current date. You can search the web for the current date.